Win95, and I think Fvwm95, automatically put the submenu to the left
of the parent menu, if it doesn't fit on the right.  This is good because
if makes it much easier to use the menu at the right edge of the screen.

Any chance of getting it into the main fvwm?  If it just requires a
patch to do so, I'll be happy to try to fit in the fvwm95 code (assuming
it exists).


