This always uses the whole rest of the line as parameter to the
play command (which can be any command, thus the parameter doesn't
have to be a filename).
If this is going into the release it needs to be documented.

If the release isn't changed, at least the old behaviour (ignoring the
rest of the line after the first word) needs to be documented.
Also I think in this case we should respect quoted parameters
("These were the times.au").

